        },
        {
            "id": "finally_block",
            "elements": [
                {
                    "type": "heading",
                    "content": "The Finally Block",
                    "properties": {
                        "level": 2
                    }
                },
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "content": "The `finally` block **always runs** - whether an error occurred or not. It's perfect for cleanup code."
                },
                {
                    "type": "code",
                    "content": "try:\n    result = 10 / 0\nexcept ZeroDivisionError:\n    print(\"Error: Division by zero\")\nfinally:\n    print(\"Cleanup complete\")",
                    "properties": {
                        "language": "python",
                        "output": "Error: Division by zero\nCleanup complete"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "content": "Even though an error occurred, the `finally` block still runs."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "finally_always_runs",
            "elements": [
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "content": "`finally` runs **no matter what** - success, error, or even if you return early."
                },
                {
                    "type": "code",
                    "content": "try:\n    number = int(\"50\")\n    print(f\"Number: {number}\")\nexcept ValueError:\n    print(\"Invalid input\")\nfinally:\n    print(\"This always runs\")",
                    "properties": {
                        "language": "python",
                        "output": "Number: 50\nThis always runs"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "content": "No error occurred, but `finally` still runs. It runs in **all cases**."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
